
Rules:

1. W have d arms (let's make them ads displayed to users each time they connect to webpage.
2. Each time a user connects to this webpage, that makes a round.
3. At each round n, we choose one ad to display to the user
4. At each round n, ad i gives reward ri(n) E {1,1}; ri(n)=1 if the user clicked on the ad i, 0 if didn't
5. Goal is to max the total reward we get over many rounds.

